22
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:26,000
Yes, you might even bring a little tone down the edge of this snow-cap and a little down there.

23
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:33,000
Now within the crevices of these canyons, put in some still darker accents here and there.

24
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:38,000
And let's darken this slope even more.

25
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:43,000
Bring all of this tone down close to the surface of that foothill also.

26
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:52,000
This Coachella Valley, where we have Palm Springs, is one of the most interesting and one of the newest developments of nature.

27
00:02:52,000 --> 00:03:01,000
